p: Secondary metabolites profiling was done by reverse phase ultra-high performance liquid chromatography mass spectrometry (RP-UHPLC-MS) analysis utilizing an Agilent 1290 Infinity UHPLC system, which was coupled with an Agilent 6520 Accurate-Mass Q-TOF mass spectrometer with a dual ESI source, as reported previously [ 27]. The details of the RP-UHPLC-MS analysis are provided in the Supplementary Material.
